Table 14. It is worth noting that some methods converge fast 
while suffering performance decay with longer train times, such as CutMix 
and SaliencyMix, and some methods perform better when train longer, such 
as ManifoldMix training 1200 epochs. Unlike these methods, AutoMix steadily 
outperforms them by a large margin regardless of the training time setting.
